CBRE Saskatchewan is pleased to present the opportunity to purchase 66 acres of development land situated in Phase 1 of the Holmwood Sector Plan. Strategically positioned along 8th Street East and the southern border of the Brighton development, Saskatoon's largest master-planned community, this site is sure to attract mixed-use commercial and high-density residential developments.
